             <span><img src="<%= asset_path('about/Sowmya_R.png') %>" class="circle_image"/></span>
            <div class="about-content">
              <h3 class="text-right">Sowmya Rajendran</h3>
              <p class="text-right">Sowmya Rajendran writes for people of all ages. She won the Sahitya
              Akademi's Bal Sahitya Puraskar this year for her book Mayil Will Not Be
              Quiet which she co-authored with Niveditha Subramaniam. Sowmya is rarely
              quiet and lives in a far more interesting make-believe world without a
              pincode for the most part.</p>
            </div>          
          </div>        
        </div>
