           <div class="even-abt">
             <span><img src="<%= asset_path('about/Anushka.png') %>" class="circle_image"/></span>
            <div class="about-content">
              <h3 class="text-right">Anushka Ravishankar</h3>
              <p class="text-right">Anushka Ravishankar has written more than thirty books for children, many of which have been published internationally and several of which have won international awards. She is now a platypus at Duckbill Books, publishing books for children and young adults.</p>
            </div>          
          </div>        
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12">
           <div class="odd-abt">
             <span><img src="<%= asset_path('about/Priya.png') %>" class="circle_image"/></span>
            <div class="about-content">
              <h3>Priya Kuriyan</h3>
              <p>Priya Kuriyan is a children's book illustrator, comic book artist and an animator. A graduate of the National Institute of design (Ahmedabad), she has directed educational films for the Sesame street show (India) and the Children's Film Society of India (CFSI) and illustrated numerous children's books for various Indian publishers. You can see her work at <a href="http://www.priyakuriyan.blogspot.com">priyakuriyan.blogspot.com</a>, <a href="http://www.pkuriyan.blogspot.com">pkuriyan.blogspot.com</a>.</p>
            </div>          
          </div>        
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
